comment:
* This class holds information about the namespace info
 * of a node.  It is used to optimize namespace lookup in
 * a generic DOM.
 * @xsl.usage internal

variables.name: m_hasXMLNSAttrs
variables.comment: Flag indicating whether this node has an XMLNS attribute

variables.name: m_hasProcessedNS
variables.comment: Flag indicating whether namespaces have been processed for this node

variables.name: m_ancestorHasXMLNSAttrs
variables.comment: Flag indicating whether one of this node's ancestor has an XMLNS attribute

variables.name: ANCESTORXMLNSUNPROCESSED
variables.comment: Constant for ancestors XMLNS atributes not processed

variables.name: ANCESTORHASXMLNS
variables.comment: Constant indicating an ancestor has an XMLNS attribute

variables.name: ANCESTORNOXMLNS
variables.comment: Constant indicating ancestors don't have an XMLNS attribute
